# Release notes for {{site.data.keyword.appconfig_short}}
{: #release-notes}

Looking for {{site.data.keyword.cloud_notm}} status, platform announcements, security bulletins, or maintenance notifications? See [{{site.data.keyword.cloud_notm}} status](https://cloud.ibm.com/status?selected=status).
{: note}

## 18 Jan 2022
{: #app-configuration-Jan1822}
{: release-note}

New Region:  Washington DC MZR
:   {{site.data.keyword.appconfig_short}} is now available in the us-east (Washington DC) multi-zone region.  Supported regions now include us-east plus us-south (Dallas), eu-gb (London), and au-syd (Sydney).

## 28 May 2021
{: #app-configuration-May2821}
{: release-note}

Introducing {{site.data.keyword.cloud_notm}} App Configuration
:   {{site.data.keyword.appconfig_short}} is Generally Available. Control features within all your applications from a central cloud dashboard. 
